and how you might like it intoned.

00:38:17.580 --> 00:38:21.180
Which words you might like to emphasize,
where you might like it to pause,

00:38:21.290 --> 00:38:23.230
where you might like
it to raise its voice,

00:38:23.250 --> 00:38:25.680
where you might like
it to lower its voice.

00:38:27.300 --> 00:38:30.200
Those guesses may not be what you intend.

00:38:30.200 --> 00:38:34.160
You can use a lot of controls to embed
in the text to give the synthesizer

00:38:34.260 --> 00:38:37.900
hints and move that pronunciation around,
that intonation, I'm sorry,

00:38:37.920 --> 00:38:38.780
that intonation around.

00:38:39.070 --> 00:38:41.600
