00:59:00.940 --> 00:59:04.590
speak optional so that the
recognizer can recognize fragments,

00:59:04.650 --> 00:59:08.430
then there's a handful of classes
available to build a language

00:59:08.430 --> 00:59:10.530
model and deal with those cases.

00:59:10.800 --> 00:59:13.890
So we've tried to set this up to
be very quick and easy to adopt,

00:59:13.990 --> 00:59:16.270
just a couple of lines
for the simple case,

00:59:16.270 --> 00:59:19.370
